{"tid":1884730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子昏迷在牛頭角油站洗手間　送院後證實死亡","createTime":"2020-02-17T19:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T05:18:02.000Z","uid":43041,"like":84,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"a94ced0c864a7fbc5a9d568cc741373cc300a615","tid":1884730,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:35:11.000Z","msg":"今日（19日）下午５時許，牛頭角祥業街與海濱道交界一油站，警方接獲一名姓潘(32歲)男子報案，指其友人暈倒在油站洗手間內，警方及救護員接報到場，將男子送往聯合醫院搶救後，證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警辺經調查，死者姓楊（35歲），初步相信事件無可疑，案件列送院時死亡，稍後安排剖屍確定死因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d34669745ecf60bcdedf9e150655962a226855","tid":1884730,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:36:32.000Z","msg":"又係心臟病？"},{"pid":"1baf2530a2d90326a668579423422a459b7fcae1","tid":1884730,"uid":26773,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:36:57.000Z","msg":"今日先有個起巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b5aeeb1660f46d3bd07a89d32b4f5572b098b6","tid":1884730,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:38:27.000Z","msg":"好恐怖"},{"pid":"0ad5f2e2b22d0e9d4aa3f430f3c474b32a5188d9","tid":1884730,"uid":198035,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:39:05.000Z","msg":"連續兩個自然暈底"},{"pid":"35abc51cfae2d1625f1be80178f88d7268c1a313","tid":1884730,"uid":192078,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"開始刺激了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cb6fb8520f1e655e1e95a8aef317524cb5f945","tid":1884730,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"35abc51cfae2d1625f1be80178f88d7268c1a313","tid":1884730,"uid":192078,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyT